metadata.description:
Each token represents a 1% stake in a $10,000 lease on a 2016 Chevrolet Equinox (VIN: 2GNALCEK3G6312989) executed in Vancouver, BC. 
Purchasers may return the token for a full refund within 2 days of purchase. 
Earnings are redeemable with Carmodity Leasing. 
Tokens may be sold back to Carmodity or any willing buyer within the constraints of BC Securities Regulations: https://www.bcsc.bc.ca/industry/issuer-regulation/raising-capital/private-early-stage-businesses
Full Token Agreement can be found here: https://ipfs.io/ipfs/QmT1sZLKMt1dQjweBfg3rN4tJ2TECGHskC16W2fQ23voJT
